  "body": "#### System information\r\n\r\nErigon version: `git_branch=devel git_tag=v2021.10.03-1548-gaee4b5378-dirty git_commit=aee4b5378871feb5886072fd80b2fc87a820384f`\r\n\r\nOS & Version: Linux\r\n\r\n#### Issue\r\n\r\nWhen running Erigon with `--prune` flags and an explicit `--snapshots true`, then `--prune` is negated:\r\n`Effective                                prune_flags= snapshot_flags=\"--snapshots=true\"`\r\n\r\nWhen running Erigon without an explicit `--snapshots true` and relying on defaults, prune flags are honored:\r\n`Effective                                prune_flags=\"--prune.h.older=90000 --prune.t.older=90000 --prune.c.older=90000 --prune.r.before=4367322\" snapshot_flags=\"--snapshots=true\"`\r\n",
